{"tid":1903567,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部人權事務特別代表劉華：中國反對酷刑決心堅定不移！","createTime":"2020-02-29T04:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T06:16:10.000Z","uid":63113,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ae0a11cae37211e92091454ddd9540323590dbf","tid":1903567,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299510698556855f868b76befe5a60d2094b65e9","tid":1903567,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T04:54:09.000Z","msg":"外交部表示，中國反對酷刑的決心堅定不移。<br />\n<br />\n外交部人權事務特別代表劉華在聯合國人權理事會會議上表示，中國六次提交《禁止酷刑公約》履約報告，表明反對酷刑。他說，中國刑法、刑事訴訟法、監獄法等多部法律法規都明確規定禁止酷刑；當前中國全面推進依法治國，深化司法改革，加強人權保障，從立法、執法、司法等領域都取得積極進展，特別是修改後的刑事訴訟法，嚴禁刑訊逼供。<br />\n<br />\n劉華又說，中國公安機關在執法辦案場所安裝監控設施，加強監督，完善落實執法過錯責任追究機制，依法保障律師執業權利和作用，努力讓人民在每宗司法案件中感受到公平正義。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511621-20200229.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511621-20200229.htm&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT26Ggm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=59e5ccff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511621-20200229.htm&h=cc92562a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511621-20200229.htm</a>"},{"pid":"936d7a352f394f8f574e367bb194f16892460f6e","tid":1903567,"uid":63113,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"「努力讓人民在每宗司法案件中感受到公平正義。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thjnueJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthjnueJ.gif&h=e5516db8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"225d5caa21fbb0efce7da6cb24bb8e151722c81b","tid":1903567,"uid":267204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T04:55:16.000Z","msg":"車厘車厘"},{"pid":"2cd0100f9b785021d5713a2577f2b1b7496d304c","tid":1903567,"ui